data.description: BIG PRICE REDUCTION!!! Tired of staring at your neighbors home from every window or do you want more space in the yard for that pool or workshop?  Then here is a rare opportunity to buy a well cared for 3 bedroom home on almost one full acre of prime real estate close to Tinker AF Base and I-40.  Potential to live in the existing home while you plan and build your home of your dreams.  Perhaps develop into multi-family housing down the road.  The possibilities with this property are only as limited as your imagination.  The rear of the property backs up to a wooded creek full of wildlife that serves as a stunning backdrop and view from the back porch and yard.  Land like this inside of city limits does not come up for sale often, so hurry and schedule a tour before it is too late.  Listing agent is family to the sellers.
